nd domiciled in ireland launched on the guggenheim fund solutions platform the fund will utilize halcyon’s investment expertise to identify public equities where there may be structural market inefficiencies or opportunities for asymmetric returns and will employ strategies including longshort relative value liquid credit and other strategies the fund will offer weekly liquidity and will launch with more than  million in capital it will leverage the existing idea generation and investment expertise across halcyon an alternative investment firm founded in  and managing approximately  billion “we are pleased to partner with guggenheim offering halcyon’s investment expertise to nonus investors in a liquid ucits format” said kevah konner coportfolio manager of the fund and vice chairman of halcyon asset management llc todd solomon coportfolio manager of the fund added “we launched the fund in response to demand for ucits strategies that attempt to capture equity upside but limit the downside and it is part of our growing liquid alternatives business which was started in  and now manages more than 2 million” guggenheim fund solutions gfs is focused on structuring and distributing alternative products that meet increasing demand for greater transparency and risk management including in the thriving liquid alternatives market gfs began operations with a focus on hedgefund managedaccount solutions and has expanded its capabilities to help managers access the surging demand for alternative ucits funds the gfs platform provides a fullservice technology and risk management infrastructure to operate alternative ucits funds and is able to leverage guggenheim partners’ global footprint “we launched our ucits platform in  with the objective of partnering with toptier managers to bring exceptional investment management capabilities into the rapidly growing liquid alternatives space” said diego winegardner senior managing director and head of guggenheim fund solutions “we are very excited to be working with halcyon a premier alternative asset manager with a long successful history in the catalystdriven space the launch of our second alternative ucits fund allows us to further expand our strategy mix and meet the diverse needs of our clients” the fund will seek to deliver attractive riskadjusted returns over the long term while attempting to limit drawdown risk through active hedging share classes are available in usd eur chf and sek press release article link what do you think    use anonymous as my name       alert me via email on new comments       todays exclusives opalesque roundtable more internalization a new paradigm for large institutional asset owners more komfie manalo opalesque asia max townshend investment director at local pensions partnership lpp believes that the uk will start to see more internalization by asset owners a trend which is already a growing in canada an opalesque exclusive fti consulting launches specialist director support services in cayman more bailey mccann opalesque new york fti consultings restructuring group is expanding its services in the cayman islands following approval of a companies management licence by the cayman islands monetary authority cima fti will be able to provide independent board directors that can manag oaktrees howard marks issues another cautionary tale more benedicte gravrand opalesque geneva oaktrees cochairman howard marks latest memo is another cautionary one that advoca the geekiest and most important number nobody is discussing more matthias knab opalesque russ koesterich head of asset allocation for blackrocks global allocation fund writes on harvest exchange history since french financial authority fines natixis € million over misuse of redemption fees more benedicte gravrand opalesque geneva the amfs enforcement committee has issued a warning to natixis asset manag todays other voices other voices ico hell is here for us investors more chris kitze technology innovator and invest